					"接下來要調整心情，集中精神。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
		},
		linkback = "0066_00254",
		linknext = "0066_00256",
		line = 3797,
	},
	["0066_00256"] = {
		{"bgm", file="bgm02", vol=100},
		{"fg", file="jun_01f_00001", file1="jun_01f_00101", file2="jun_01f_00203", file4="jun_01f_00401", path=":fg/jun_01f/", id=30, ch="淳之介", mw="mw", mode=1, sync=0, x=-5, y=-5, lv=1},
		{"text"},
		text = {
			ja = {
				{
					name = {"淳之介"},
					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					name = {"淳之介", "Junnosuke"},
					"“Well then... my esteemed student council president! Please help me study! I’m counting on you!”",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					name = {"淳之介"},
					"“那么……学生会长，今天的读书会就麻烦你了……！”",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			tw = {
				{
					name = {"淳之介"},
					"「那麼……學生會長，今天的讀書會就麻煩妳了……！」",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
		},
		linkback = "0066_00255",
		linknext = "0066_00257",
		line = 3810,
	},
	["0066_00257"] = {
		{"fg", file="tohka_02m_00001", file1="tohka_02m_00101", file2="tohka_02m_00202", path=":fg/tohka_02m/", id=8, lv=7, head="tohka_02m", ch_origin="桐香", ch="桐香8", mw="mw", sync=0, mode=3, x=-5, y=-5},
		{"transitiontime", time=300},
		{"fgact", ch="桐香8", id=8, act="振動下", loop=1, size=12.5, time=500, ease="easeinout_sine"},
		{"text"},
		text = {
			vo = {
				{"vo", file="tohka1571", path=":vo/", ch="touka"},
			},
			ja = {
				{
					name = {"桐香"},
					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					name = {"桐香", "Touka"},
					"“With pleasure. Leave it to me, Tachibana!”",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					name = {"桐香"},
					"“好的。请多指教，前辈。”",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			tw = {
				{
					name = {"桐香"},
					"「好的。請多指教，前輩。」",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
		},
		linkback = "0066_00256",
		linknext = "0066_00258",
		line = 3825,
	},
	["0066_00258"] = {
		{"text"},
		text = {
			ja = {
				{
					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"My lovely girlfriend is quite the character. Whenever she talks to me, a lot of it goes right over my head.",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"我的女朋友虽然很奇怪，常常会说出一些难懂的话。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			tw = {
				{
					"我的女朋友雖然很奇怪，常常會說出一些難懂的話。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
		},
		linkback = "0066_00257",
		linknext = "0066_00259",
		line = 3835,
	},
	["0066_00259"] = {
		{"text"},
		text = {
			ja = {
				{
					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"But no matter what she says, it’s clear to me that she is simply amazing. She’s the student council president and, quite literally, a genius.",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"但，再怎么说她都是学生会长，而且说她是“天才”也一点都不夸张。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			tw = {
				{
					"但，再怎麼說她都是學生會長，而且說她是「天才」也一點都不誇張。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
		},
		linkback = "0066_00258",
		linknext = "0066_00260",
		line = 3845,
	},
	["0066_00260"] = {
		{"text"},
		text = {
			ja = {
				{
					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"I’ve heard that she is not only first in her class, but even ranks in the top 50 students nationally.",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"成绩是学校里第一名，全国的模拟考试也都是前50名以内。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			tw = {
				{
					"成績是學校裡第一名，全國的模擬考試也都是前50名以內。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
		},
		linkback = "0066_00259",
		linknext = "0066_00261",
		line = 3855,
	},
	["0066_00261"] = {
		{"text"},
		text = {
			ja = {
				{
					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"Plus, she has great natural instincts. No matter what challenge she’s up against, she can overcome it with ease.",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"头脑也好，什么都难不倒她的感觉。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			tw = {
				{
					"頭腦也好，什麼都難不倒她的感覺。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
		},
		linkback = "0066_00260",
		linknext = "0066_00262",
		line = 3865,
	},
	["0066_00262"] = {
		{"text"},
		text = {
			ja = {
				{
					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"On top of that, she’s an amazing public speaker, an adept problem-solver, and can think on her feet.",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"擅长说话，也善于发现问题，脑袋运转得很快。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			tw = {
				{
					"擅長說話，也善於發現問題，腦袋運轉得很快。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
		},
		linkback = "0066_00261",
		linknext = "0066_00263",
		line = 3875,
	},
	["0066_00263"] = {
		{"text"},
		text = {
			ja = {
				{
					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"She’s head and shoulders above everyone in school. Yet she seems to know exactly what the student body needs, and she never fails to provide it to them.",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"以站在领导学生的立场上来说，她具备了所有需要的条件。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			tw = {
				{
					"以站在領導學生的立場上來說，她具備了所有需要的條件。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
		},
		linkback = "0066_00262",
		linknext = "0066_00264",
		line = 3885,
	},
	["0066_00264"] = {
		{"text"},
		text = {
			ja = {
				{
					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"So I am incredibly surprised to find out that a young woman this talented... could be this shitty at teaching.",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"所以完全没想到对于教别人，她居然这么不擅长──",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			tw = {
				{
					"所以完全沒想到對於教別人，她居然這麼不擅長──",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
		},
		linkback = "0066_00263",
		linknext = "0066_00265",
		line = 3895,
	},
	["0066_00265"] = {
		{"bgm", stop=1},
		{"se", id=0, loop=0, file="se_a141"},
		{"fg", file="tohka_02m_00001", file1="tohka_02m_00101", file2="tohka_02m_00228", path=":fg/tohka_02m/", id=8, lv=7, head="tohka_02m", ch_origin="桐香", ch="桐香8", mw="mw", sync=0, mode=3, x=-5, y=-5},
		{"transitiontime", time=300},
		{"text"},
